Symbol.Script_3D:
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then end if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then gs_resol = 12
if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
pen gs_cont_pen add a/2,b,0
hotspot 0,0,0,1 hotspot 0,0,a/2,2 hotspot 0,0,a,3 hotspot -a/2,0,a/2,4 hotspot a/2,0,a/2,5
hotspot 0,-b,0,6 hotspot 0,-b,a,7 hotspot -a/2,-b,a/2,8 hotspot a/2,-b,a/2,9
addz a/2 rotx 90
material framat resol gs_resol prism_ 14, B, a/2, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0.0, 180.0, 4000, -a/2, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180.0, 4001, a/2, 0.0, -1,
a/2-frw, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0.0, 180.0, 4000, -a/2+frw, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180.0, 4001, a/2-frw, 0.0, -1
material plamat
prism_ 7, B/6, a/2-frw, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0.0, 180.0, 4000, -a/2+frw, 0, 79, 0, 0, 900, 0, 180.0, 4001, a/2-frw, 0.0, -1
if gs_resol < 5 then mul 0.70, 0.70, 1 else if gs_resol < 7 then mul 0.85, 0.85, 1 else mul 1, 1, 1 endif endif
addz B/6 + 0.0001
material numat for n = 1 to 4 prism_ 5, 0, -a/150,a/2-frw-a/80-a/15,15, a/150,a/2-frw-a/80-a/15,15, a/150,a/2-frw-a/80,15, -a/150,a/2-frw-a/80,15, -a/150,a/2-frw-a/80-a/15,-1 rotz 90 next n del 4
for i = 1 to 2 rotz 30 for n = 1 to 4 prism_ 5, 0, -a/180,a/2-frw-a/80-a/20,15, a/180,a/2-frw-a/80-a/20,15, a/180,a/2-frw-a/80,15, -a/180,a/2-frw-a/80,15, -a/180,a/2-frw-a/80-a/20,-1 rotz 90 next n next i del 10
if numb then define style "your text" fontType ,a*50,5,0 set style "your text"
rotz -30 for t = 1 to 12 addy a/2 - frw - a/9 rotz t * 30 text 0, 0, t del 2 rotz -30 next t del 13 endif
del 1
material hamat addz B/6
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then resolnum = 5 else resolnum = 12 endif
resol resolnum cylind B/2,A/40
addz B/3
rotz -mnt*6
prism_ 7,0, -a/100,a/40,15, a/100,a/40,15, a/80,a/5,15, a/200,a/2-frw-a/40,15, -a/200,a/2-frw-a/40,15, -a/80,a/5,15, -a/100,a/40,-1
del 1
addz -b/6 rotz -hrs*30-mnt/2 prism_ 7,0, -a/100,a/40,15, a/100,a/40,15, a/70,a/6,15, a/300,a/2-frw-a/7,15, -a/300,a/2-frw-a/7,15, -a/70,a/6,15, -a/100,a/40,-1
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Clock.gsm
pen gs_cont_pen
add2 a/2,b
hotspot2 0, 0, 1
fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 5, 1+2+4+64,gs_fill_pen,gs_back_pen, -a/2,0,1, -a/2,-b,1, a/2,-b,1, a/2,0,1, -a/2,0,-1 del 1
call "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" parameters all
Symbol.Script_1D: ! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2 DLEV3D_DRAFT = 3
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
!Hide all parameters from UI hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
values "hrs" RANGE [0, 23] values "mnt" RANGE [0, 59]
parameters zzyzx = a lock "zzyzx"
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values "gs_resol" range [3,)
if gs_cont_pen = 0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=7 if gs_fill_pen = 0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then hideparameter "gs_resol" if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF then hideparameter "gs_shadow", "gs_resol"
if not(numb) then hideparameter "fontType"
parameters gs_font_size= abs(gs_font_size) values "gs_font_size" range (0,]
